  array('id' => '674661311','title' => 'Linux Kernel Development, 3rd Edition','isbn' => '9780672329463','description' => 'Linux Kernel Development details the design and implementation of the Linux kernel, presenting the content in a manner that is beneficial to those writing and developing kernel code, as well as to programmers seeking to better understand the operating system and become more efficient and productive in their coding.

