  array('id' => '101245959','title' => 'Learning Android, 2nd Edition','isbn' => '9781449319236','description' => 'Want to build apps for Android devices? This book is the perfect way to master the fundamentals. Written by experts who have taught this mobile platform to hundreds of developers in large organizations and startups alike, this gentle introduction shows experienced object-oriented programmers how to use Android\'s basic building blocks to create user interfaces, store data, connect to the network, and more.

