  array('id' => '1290301462','title' => 'Learning PHP, MySQL, JavaScript, and CSS, 2nd Edition','isbn' => '9781449319267','description' => 'Learn how to build interactive, data-driven websites - even if you don\'t have any previous programming experience. If you know how to build static sites with HTML, this popular guide will help you tackle dynamic web programming. You\'ll get a thorough grounding in today\'s core open source technologies: PHP, MySQL, JavaScript, and CSS.

